div.p:
Please cable Department the following: 
                                    (1)

The number of Russian military forces cooperating with the
                                        Czechs west of Irkutsk, including European Russia;
                                    (2)

Their organization and to what extent it is
                                        developed;


                                    (3)

Their supplies, what they are and how obtained;
                                    (4)

Their morale;
                                    (5)

Whether they are subject to proper military
                                        discipline;
                                    (6)

Whether they are representative of the real sentiment of
                                        the Siberian people;
                                    (7)

Who are their leaders.
